responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "B9E3D973426FB9F5CF874FB8AA20E79F", "Yes, this is mine, I remember it with the clarity of my anger. But I am not a menace, yes, I am sure of this. The recollection of my fate, however, is full of doubt. Only fragments appear, but I think I may have caught a glimpse. It is the Lowlander\'s garb, the infernal apostates. He had stabbed me from behind, so I cannot remember his face.")
name: MADD_0008_BrotherMindel_23
